I have been around the motor industry for quite a long time and I can honestly say I have never driven a Mahindra before last week, when the Indian manufacturer’s new Pik-Up S11 automatic bakkie was launched. My ignorance when it comes to the brand and its products is right up there, but I was told that Mahindra was recognised as South Africa’s fastest-growing brand in 2019. According to the National Association of Automobile Manufacturers (NAAMSA), Mahindra grew by 28.7% last year, while the overall market declined by 2.8% in the same period. So, it must be doing something right,...